                <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.7</sparkle:shortVersionString>
                <description><![CDATA[<ul><li>Smart clipboard: app-aware tab that surfaces items you've copied from or pasted into the current app</li><li>Tabbed clipboard panel with Smart, Recent, and Pinned views</li><li>Arrow key and Tab/Shift-Tab keyboard shortcuts for cycling clipboard tabs</li><li>Re-copied clipboard items now reflect the latest source app and timestamp</li><li>Dock right-click menu now lists all open windows for quick access</li><li>Ollama custom endpoint and selected models now persist reliably across app restarts</li></ul>]]></description>
